r: When my class is displayed in Fullscreen mode (like shown in the code above) then this error is generated. I have looked it up, but havent found a solution yet</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Possibly youre getting a paint event when the windows is not exposed. But Im just guessing here.</p>\n","timestamp":"2016-05-16T22:23:45.099Z","user":{"username":"kshegunov","userslug":"kshegunov","email":"kshegunov@gmail.com","picture":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/9296f2b3c8c9866793455bf2c26a6195?size=192&d=mm","uid":25369,"icon:text":"K","icon:bgColor":"#009688"},"index":6},"tags":[{"value":"framebuffer","color":"","bgColor":"","score":10},{"value":"vsync","color":"","bgColor":"","score":3}],"isOwner":false,"unread":true,"unreplied":false},{"tid":67122,"uid":11759,"cid":10,"mainPid":327679,"title":"<span class=\"unanswered\"><i class=\"fa fa-question-circle\"></i> Unsolved</span> camera capture BA81 format","slug":"67122/camera-capture-ba81-format","timestamp":1463419627418,"lastposttime":1463436994987,"postcount":2,"viewcount":18,"locked":false,"deleted":false,"pinned":false,"isQuestion":1,"isSolved":0,"teaserPid":"327720","relativeTime":"2016-05-16T17:27:07.418Z","lastposttimeISO":"2016-05-16T22:16:34.987Z","category":{"cid":10,"name":"General and Desktop","icon":"fa-laptop","bgColor":"#80c342","color":"#FFFFFF","slug":"10/general-and-desktop","disabled":false},"user":{"username":"gfxx","userslug":"gfxx","email":"giorgiofoga@hotmail.it","picture":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/c36c952b8cf204d4c309d4c455ce3727?size=192&d=mm","fullname":"giorgio foga","signature":"","reputation":5,"postcount":53,"banned":0,"status":"offline","uid":11759,"icon:text":"G","icon:bgColor":"#ff5722"},"teaser":{"pid":327720,"uid":5578,"tid":67122,"content":"<p>Hi,</p>\n<p>You should also check with GStreamer directly to see if it works. Qts multimedia backend is GStreamer on Linux.</p>\n","timestamp":"2016-05-16T22:16:34.987Z","user":{"username":"SGaist","userslug":"sgaist","email":"samuel.gaist@ede